Panarion is a curated collection of Free and Open Source Software (FOSS) tools and resources for self-hosting, privacy, and digital autonomy.  
It lists essential open projects for productivity, communication, media, and security — a compact reference for building your own independent tech ecosystem.

- [KeePassXC](https://keepassxc.org/) — secure, local password manager  
- [SendMe](https://www.iroh.computer/sendme) — lightweight, open-source file sharing tool
